{"tid":2173170,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"2017參選政綱（青年篇） 誠邀青年 並肩同行","createTime":"2020-08-25T05:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T05:34:05.000Z","uid":50457,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c75d662a003f1754963edc010d1d2437e8192bb8","tid":2173170,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T05:34:05.000Z","msg":"‧ 與青年一起解決學業、事業及置業的困難。<br />\n\r<br />\n‧ 設立由政務司司長主持的「青年發展委員會」，以增加統籌及執行能力。<br />\n\r<br />\n‧ 增加議政機會：行政長官和主要官員定期訪問學校，以及透過各溝通渠道，包括社交媒體，與青年對話。<br />\n\r<br />\n‧ 增加論政機會，引入「自薦委任」制度。<br />\n\r<br />\n‧ 增加參政機會：把中策組改組成政策及項目統籌組，並聘用20至30名青年。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}